      • run

        public void run(HasPlansAndId<T,I> person)
        Description copied from interface: GenericPlanStrategy
        Adds a person to this strategy to be handled. It is not required that the person is immediately handled during this method-call (e.g. when using multi-threaded strategy-modules). This method ensures that an unscored plan is selected if the person has such a plan ("optimistic behavior").
        Specified by:
        run in interface GenericPlanStrategy<T extends BasicPlan,I>
        See Also:
        GenericPlanStrategy.finish()
